                          Forestry

Forestry gathers construction wood from marked timber stands in the
Kingswood. Buy a forestry axe in the profession general store, find a visible
harvestable stand, and use:

  chop tree

The stand is exhausted after a successful harvest and returns when its virtual
room resets. Forestry skill increases yield and can produce fine, superior, or
masterwork oak, ash, and pine timber. Timber is saved automatically rather
than carried as a normal inventory object.

  reagents wood       Show saved timber, planks, and framing bundles.
  carpentry list      Show timber refinement and crafting plans.
  help carpentry      Explain refinement, furniture, and construction supply.
